-- John Edwards Judge Declares Mistrial in Campaign Payment Case
-- B y   S o p h i a   P e a r s o n
-- 2012-05-31T20:23:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-31/john-edwards-judge-declares-mistrial-in-campaign-payment-case.html
The judge in  John Edwards 's federal
criminal trial for campaign-finance violations declared a
mistrial after the jury was unable to reach a unanimous verdict
on all but one count. They found the former U.S. senator not
guilty of a single count of receiving illegal contributions.  To contact the reporter on this story:
